import PyPDF2

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/28-SPIN/SPIN/paper.pdf'
reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(pdf_path)
num_pages = len(reader.pages)

# Try to extract the first 5 pages for loss function details
text = ''
for i in range(min(5, num_pages)):
    text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n'

print(text[:3000])
